reviewText: Loved it, reminded me of the good old days.

I got this to show on a tour bus.  Everyone really enjoyed it (I was pretty sure of that - it's Charlie Prose).  Anything of Charlie's is
always a hit.
Love Charlie!  This DVD quality good;  but I found this one not as funny as he usually is.  Music at the end is Fabulous!  I ordered it because of the location he filmed it.
I bought and gave this as a gift to my parents for Christmas......I have NOT seen it myself but based on their reviews and another family member who saw it, I give it 5 stars.
I am a travel cooridator and need fun videos for my customers to view while on tours. Showed Love And Laughter and eveyone loved it.

Not a DVD that you can buy in a local store.  Saw it on a bus trip and
it really is quite funny without using dirty language.
